channel.title: Oh wow, I actually made something
channel.description:
God, after a few months of nearly nothing, I made THIS! :D
[img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/2844/renderjy.png[/img]
(keep in mind I still keep my models poly-efficient for servers <.<)
Its not all too great, but I'm using a new method of modeling that I may share soon, and considering how I'm making it, its working very well. If anyone really wants a release, PM me or post for it and I'll ad a DL.
Here's a weild view for anyone interested: [img]http://img191.imageshack.us/img191/592/renderwd.png[/img]
